          <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link" href="/streams">Streams</a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link" href="/find">Find College</a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link" href="/contact">Contact Us</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>



  
  <div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="content">
      <h1>WELCOME!</h1>
      <p>Welcome to our College Recommender website! We specialize in offering tailored college suggestions based on your location and percentile. Our platform provides you with accurate, up-to-date information, helping you explore the best educational options with ease. Whether you're looking for an institution close to home or exploring opportunities further afield, our user-friendly interface ensures a seamless experience. Let us guide you to the ideal college that aligns with your academic goals and ambitions!</p>

