    <div class="about-section mt-5">
      <h2>ABOUT US</h2>
      <p>Welcome to College Recommender, your user-friendly platform for finding the perfect college! We simplify your search based on location, chosen streams, and CET percentiles, helping students discover educational opportunities that align with their aspirations. Your support enhances this experience, enabling us to offer personalized recommendations and valuable insights into various colleges and courses. Join us as we guide you toward a bright and successful academic journey!</p>
